SELECT policyreinsurancestats.SystemId, policyreinsurancestats.id, policyreinsurancestats.StatSequence, policyreinsurancestats.StatSequenceReplace, policyreinsurancestats.PolicyRef, policyreinsurancestats.PolicyNumber, policyreinsurancestats.PolicyVersion, policyreinsurancestats.TransactionNumber, policyreinsurancestats.EffectiveDt, policyreinsurancestats.ExpirationDt, policyreinsurancestats.CombinedKey, policyreinsurancestats.AddDt, policyreinsurancestats.BookDt, policyreinsurancestats.TransactionEffectiveDt, policyreinsurancestats.AccountingDt, policyreinsurancestats.WrittenPremiumAmt, policyreinsurancestats.WrittenCommissionAmt, policyreinsurancestats.EarnDays, policyreinsurancestats.InforceChangeAmt, policyreinsurancestats.PolicyYear, policyreinsurancestats.TermDays, policyreinsurancestats.InsuranceTypeCd, policyreinsurancestats.StartDt, policyreinsurancestats.EndDt, policyreinsurancestats.StatusCd, policyreinsurancestats.NewRenewalCd, policyreinsurancestats.AnnualStatementLineCd, policyreinsurancestats.ReinsuranceName, policyreinsurancestats.MasterSubInd, policyreinsurancestats.ReinsuranceItemName, policyreinsurancestats.ProviderCd, policyreinsurancestats.TransactionCd, policyreinsurancestats.StateCd, policyreinsurancestats.ReinsuranceGroupId, policyreinsurancestats.ProductVersionIdRef, policyreinsurancestats.CarrierGroupCd, policyreinsurancestats.CarrierCd, policyreinsurancestats.PolicyStatusCd, policyreinsurancestats.ProductName, policyreinsurancestats.PolicyTypeCd, policyreinsurancestats.PolicyGroupCd, policyreinsurancestats.CustomerRef, policyreinsurancestats.ReinsuranceCoverageGroupCd, policyreinsurancestats.PolicySource, policyreinsurancestats.ReinsurerCode, policyreinsurancestats.MajorPerilCd, policyreinsurancestats.StateLineCd,
policyreinsurancestats.UpdateTimestamp
FROM
 policyreinsurancestats 
 where policyref in
 (select policyref from policyreinsurancestats
 where
 updatetimestamp >= '$$m_strtdt' 
 and updatetimestamp < '$$m_Enddt'
)
